abstract: Graeme Storm shoots 10-under-par 67 to share lead with Ross Fisher and Charl Schwartzel in European Open.
lead_paragraph: Graeme Storm holed out for eagle on the back nine for a share of the lead at the halfway point of the European Open in Bad Griesbach, Germany.

headline.main: Three Tied for First at European Open
